@startuml shawntabrizi_Ethereum-Twitter-Bounty

!define RECTANGLE class

RECTANGLE "Web Interface" as UI {
    [HTML/CSS]
    [JavaScript]
    [Bootstrap]
}

RECTANGLE "Web3.js" as Web3 {
    [TruffleContract]
}

RECTANGLE "Smart Contracts" as Contracts {
    [TwitterBounty]
    [TwitterOracle]
}

RECTANGLE "Ethereum Blockchain" as Blockchain

RECTANGLE "Oracle Service" as Oracle {
    [Provable Things]
}

RECTANGLE "Twitter API" as TwitterAPI

UI --> Web3 : uses
Web3 --> Contracts : interacts with
Contracts --> Blockchain : deployed on
TwitterOracle --> Oracle : requests data
Oracle --> TwitterAPI : fetches tweets
Oracle --> TwitterOracle : returns data

note right of UI
  Provides user interface for
  bounty management
end note

note right of Web3
  Facilitates communication
  between UI and blockchain
end note

note right of Contracts
  Manages bounty lifecycle
  and tweet verification
end note

note right of Oracle
  Retrieves tweet content
  from Twitter API
end note

@enduml